						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">lidnariq wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">2 ICs:<br />Inverter + RAM<br />→ Map 8KB RAM into PPU $0xxx and $2xxx for 4KB CHR-RAM slice and 4-screen mirroring, inverter makes <tt style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding:3px; background-color: #3355aa; color: white;">NOT A12</tt> to decode 4KB ROM (or 4KB window) in $1xxx</div><br />Wow. Clever. That allows a separate background bank at $1000 for each locale type while still allowing arbitrary combination of sprites ($0000).</div>

