						<div class="postbody">The reset circuit as I described was used in <a href="http://bootgod.dyndns.org:7777/profile.php?id=1390" class="postlink">Caltron 6-in-1</a>. A variant that used <tt style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding:3px; background-color: #3355aa; color: white;">CPU A0</tt> instead of <tt style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding:3px; background-color: #3355aa; color: white;">M2</tt> was used in <a href="http://bootgod.dyndns.org:7777/profile.php?id=1362" class="postlink">Maxi 15</a>.</div>

