					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">While talking about the UxROM-512 thread, I thought of another one:<br /><br />2 ICs: UNROM without bus conflicts:<br /> use 74'02 instead of 74'32<br />Reverse 16KiB slices before burning. Use last NOR gate to invert RnW to produce /RD and connect that to the ROM's /OE pin.<br />Correspondingly, the maximum size is now only 128KiB.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

